	INNER JOIN INFORMATICS.dbo.AQR_VISTAR AS aqr ON (LTRIM(RTRIM(ISNULL(inf.NPIis,'')))) = (LTRIM(RTRIM(ISNULL(aqr.ID,'')))) -- IMPORT FROM SQL01.VIP aka 'VISTAR' TO FIX AS [ACCREDITATION_QUALITY_REPORT] see 'AQR_VISTAR_20180711.xlsx' ,CAST(NULL AS varchar(100)) AS [ACCREDITATION_QUALITY_REPORT] -- ANOTHER REVERSAL per S. COLEMAN email ON 20170522 ANOTHER ADD per SCOLEMAN In the Provider Directory Team meeting today, we agreed to make a slight change.  We realized that we must show the individual link to the accredited source for each hospital MC & CMC directories.We will keep Accredited & Accredited by fields.  Please remove the quality fields from all facilities for printed and online directories.  We will keep the star rating data in Vistar just in case it is asked for in the future.This field will be replaced by “Accreditation & Quality Report:” for hospitals only.  I’ve placed the hyperlink name in 3.	Accreditation and Quality Summary will hyperlink to the address provided by the data.  ON 20170419
WHERE inf.[ACCREDITATION_QUALITY_REPORT] IS NULL
