,spe.[ACCREDITATION_QUALITY_REPORT] -- ANOTHER ADD per SCOLEMAN In the Provider Directory Team meeting today, we agreed to make a slight change.  We realized that we must show the individual link to the accredited source for each hospital MC & CMC directories.We will keep Accredited & Accredited by fields.  Please remove the quality fields from all facilities for printed and online directories.  We will keep the star rating data in Vistar just in case it is asked for in the future.This field will be replaced by “Accreditation & Quality Report:” for hospitals only.  I’ve placed the hyperlink name in 'board_cert. notes' AS [ACCREDITATION_QUALITY_REPORT] -- 3.	Accreditation and Quality Summary will hyperlink to the address provided by the data. field for a place holder.  This field format should allow in pdf and online to link to actual address.  Data is in  Paradise Valley Hospital (v9514) and Radys Children’s Hospital (v9509) records.  We will add the link in the other hospitals tomorrow. Please call me if you have any questions.  ON 20170419
,spe.lookup_key
,spe.[URL_WEBSITE]
,spe.[TTY] AS [AFTERHOURS_PHONE]
,spe.[FAXnumber],spe.[EMAILis]
,[CCSPaneledProvider] -- ADD TO FAC / SITE [TABLE(S)] AS OF 20220215
,[MedicaidMedicareFlag]
,[MMF]
,[FUTURE_TERM]
,[Telehealth_Indicator]
,[COUNTY] -- C007: APPLICABLE TO PROVIDERS ONLY!!! ADD - ON PER EMAIL FROM MS JOHANNA BASED UPON DHCS FINDING (LEVERAGE: APL 25-014 AND OR "PROVDIR Telehealth Indicator evips location .msg")
INTO INFORMATICS.dbo.PROVDIR_HOSGENERALACUTE
